prompts.frontCover: A dynamic comic book cover featuring the couple from the photo as superheroes. Lao Lao, in the foreground, strikes a powerful and heroic pose, wearing a stylized version of her blue sweatshirt with a custom superhero emblem on the chest. She has a confident, smiling expression. Jordan is behind her, depicted as her trusty sidekick, in his tan hoodie, giving a cheerful thumbs-up and a wide, supportive smile. They are set against a vibrant, explosive "POW!" style background with Ben-Day dots, bold action lines, and a sunburst of bright yellows, reds, and blues. The overall style is flat 2D art with thick black outlines and saturated colors, reminiscent of classic comics. In the center, a white, jagged-edged comic book-style speech bubble contains the text "Happy Birthday, My Amazing Lao Lao!" written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script.
